<p>The RecycleBIM Project aims to foster a collaborative, international initiative focused on establishing an integrated framework for the circularity of raw materials. Leveraging the power of Building Information Modelling (BIM) methodology, the project seeks to promote circularity-oriented and sustainable practices within the construction industry. Curious to learn more? Check out our testimonial video for further insights!
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UCZrVFRP8lw</p>

